ABOUT
This remote is about tools for comparing similarity between two documents in massive dataset.

The program first extracts all k-grams from documents, forming a feature set for each document. Then Jaccard similarity between two sets are computed using Minhash (a kind of locality sensitive hashing).

Reference: http://infolab.stanford.edu/~ullman/mmds/ch3.pdf


